  <brief_title>A Study Assessing Efficacy of Brivaracetam in Subjects With Persistent Pain After Shingles (Post-herpetic Neuralgia)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double Blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Study, for the Assessment of Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of Brivaracetam at the Doses of 200 mg/Day and 400 mg/Day, in Subjects (at Least 18 Years Old) Suffering From Post-herpetic Neuralgia (PHN)</official_title>
