  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study will assess efficacy, safety and tolerability of brivaracetam in post-herpetic
      neuralgia (PHN). Duration of 7 weeks divided into 3 periods with no up-titration, nor
      down-titration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
